{
  "stem": "21786.9",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was in Hamburg at that point in time.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So first I went there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I found out that there is a special kind of department of citizenship, which gathers the lists of liberated prisoners from all over the-- all over Europe.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Whether there is anything from Hamburg, which it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She wasn't-- there was a list from the Hamburg-- from Hamburg, but she was not on the list.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I got myself an apartment, according to the wishes which we had with Eva that we will look for something like my offices upstairs-- one big room, a modern bathroom, in a modern building, with elevator, with modern kitchen, with everything.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I got it allotted from the Czech authorities.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was seized from some Germans.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I didn't [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I returned, but somebody was living there, and it would be very difficult to dislodge them.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they gave me a replacement apartment.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they gave a replacement apartment to my mother when she returned.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I was going to this address simply looking for Eva regularly, every day.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And about 10 days later, I found out that there were two guys there who was-- who are saying that they were going to Hamburg to bring the list of the liberated prisoners plus one very kind of prominent Czech writer who was liberated in Kiel, K-I-E-L, in a camp.",
      "word_count": 50
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so I said, I'm going with you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, hold it, hold it, hold it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We need an interpreter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said, you just found one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I proclaimed myself for an interpreter.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They slept over in my place, and then we entered in a truck, which was a Chevrolet 1922, which did not make the mountains quite.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But we got through the Russians, and we got it repaired.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
